verbose_text: Similarly as neobacillamide A XREF_BIBR, bacillamide C could be derived from amino acids alanine, cysteine and tryptophan through NRPS biosynthesis strategy, which was supported by the finding of a NRPS gene cluster (7, 011 bp) by sequencing the genome of B. atrophaeus C89 (Genbank No. JQ 687535) XREF_BIBR.
